---
title: Double Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Spiced Wedges with Burger Sauce & Avocado Salad
description: A plant-based version of chicken tenders, yes it can be done. A side of golden wedges to dip in a burger sauce (it’s great for the chicken tenders too!) will make your mouth water in no time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65765008a65f6d71569fae3e-70b33925.jpeg
